Quarter: The financial quarter and year for which the employee turnover rate is reported (e.g., Q3 2025).
Employee_Turnover_Rate: The percentage of employees who left the company during the specified quarter.
Total_Employees_Start: The total number of employees at the beginning of the quarter.
Total_Employees_End: The total number of employees at the end of the quarter.
Voluntary_Exits: The number of employees who left the company voluntarily during the quarter.
Involuntary_Exits: The number of employees who left the company involuntarily during the quarter.
New_Hires: The number of new employees hired during the quarter.
